---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const meta = {
  title: 'Loumarc Signs | High-end full service sign experts | Review us',
  canonicalURL: 'https://loumarcsigns.com/review/',
};
---
<Layout meta={meta}>
    <a href="#main" class="sr-only sr-only-focusable">Skip to content</a>
  <Header />
  <div class="section spot-color-gray">
    <svg
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="slant"
      viewBox="0 0 1440 67"
      preserveAspectRatio="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <path d="M0,66.398L1440,18.066L1440,0L0,0L0,66.398Z"></path>
    </svg>
    <div class="section__inner region">
      <div class="center">
        <div class="box">
          <h1>Our customers' satisfaction is paramount to our success.</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <svg
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="slant"
      viewBox="0 0 1440 67"
      preserveAspectRatio="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <path d="M0,66.398L1440,18.066L1440,0L0,0L0,66.398Z"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <main id="main">
        <article class="content region flow prose">
        <p>We hope that you are pleased with our service and your signs. We look forward to helping you again in the future. </p>
        <p>Below is a list of our social properties. If you could share with the world what compelled you to choose Loumarc Signs, or a experience that stands out from working with us, we'd greatly appreciate it.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://g.page/Loumarc-Signs/review?mt">Google</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/loumarcsigns/reviews/">Facebook</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/loumarc-signs/about/">LinkedIn</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.angi.com/companylist/us/nj/hillsborough/loumarc-signs-reviews-3826544.htm">Angi</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.yelp.com/biz/loumarc-signs-hillsborough">Yelp</a></li>
        </ul>
        </article>
    </main>
</Layout>